ability.name: Infernal Chains
ability.bonus: After a brief delay, Aatrox pulls in the farthest enemies then slams the ground, dealing magic damage to all adjacent enemies.

ability.name: Five-Point Strike
ability.bonus: Akali throws kunai at her target, dealing magic damage.

ability.name: Shield-Blast
ability.bonus: Annie blasts a cone of fire dealing magic damage to enemies in front of her, then creates a shield for herself for a few seconds.

ability.name: Warlord's Divide
ability.bonus: Azir charges forward with a wall of soldiers, knocking back enemies hit and dealing magic damage. After their charge, the wall of soldiers remains in place in front of Azir for 3 seconds as impassable terrain. Any spearmen from the General trait will accompany Azir for the charge and position themselves to protect him afterwards.

ability.name: Spider Form
ability.bonus: Elise transforms into a spider, gaining bonus maximum health and causing her attacks to restore health.

ability.name: Riposte
ability.bonus: Fiora enters a defensive stance for 1.5 seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy spell effects. As she exits this stance, she ripostes, dealing magic damage to a nearby enemy and stunning them for a few seconds.

ability.name: Judgment
ability.bonus: Garen spins his sword for 4 seconds, reducing incoming magic damage by 80% and dealing magic damage to nearby enemies over the duration.

ability.name: Bladestorm
ability.bonus: Irelia launches a barrage of blades infront of her, dealing magic damage and applying on-hit effects. Enemies hit are disarmed for a few seconds.

ability.name: Eye of the Storm
ability.bonus: Janna shields the lowest health allies for 4 seconds. Shielded allies gain Attack Damage for the duration.

ability.name: Dragon Strike
ability.bonus: Jarvan strikes the furthest target within 3 hexes with his spear and pulls himself towards them, dealing magic damage to units he passes through and knocking them up and stunning them for 1 second.

ability.name: Counter Strike
ability.bonus: Jax dodges all incoming attacks for 2 seconds, then strikes all nearby units, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.

ability.name: Rend
ability.bonus: Passive: Kalista's spears remain in her target, each one capable of dealing a percent of the target's max health as magic damage when she removes them. Kalista will remove the spears when doing so would kill the target.

ability.name: Death Lotus
ability.bonus: Katarina channels for 2.5 seconds, throwing knives at nearby enemies, dealing magic damage over the duration and reducing healing by 50% to her targets for 5 seconds.

ability.name: Slicing Maelstrom
ability.bonus: Kennen summons a storm around him, dealing magic damage over 3 seconds and stunning enemies inside of it for 1.5 seconds.

ability.name: God Fist
ability.bonus: Lee Sin punches his target, dealing magic damage, knocking them back to the edge of the battlefield, and stunning them for a few seconds. Any enemies the target collides with during the knockback receive half the damage and stunned for 1 second. If the target cannot be pushed back any further, they are knocked out of the battlefield instead, removing them from combat. If the target is still alive, Lee Sin will dash to them.

ability.name: Wild Growth
ability.bonus: Lulu makes a low health ally giant, granting them bonus health and knocking up adjacent enemies near them for 1 seconds.

ability.name: Bramble Smash
ability.bonus: Maokai smashes enemies infront of him, dealing magic damage and slowing their Attack Speed by 50% for 3 seconds.

ability.name: Javelin Toss
ability.bonus: Nidalee throws her Javelin at the furthest enemy, dealing magic damage plus 20% per hex traveled.

ability.name: Consume
ability.bonus: Willump bites his target, dealing magic damage. If Willump's target has less Health than him before the bite, it deals an additional 50% damage and deals true damage instead.

ability.name: Firecracker
ability.bonus: Sejuani sets off a giant firecracker. After a short delay, enemies caught within are dealt magic damage and stunned for a few seconds.

ability.name: Showstopper
ability.bonus: Sett grabs his target and slams them forward, dealing a percent of his target's maximum health in magic damage to all enemies in a large area. Enemies further from the epicenter take less damage.

ability.name: Shadow Dash
ability.bonus: Shen dashes past his target, shielding himself against damage and taunting all adjacent enemies.

ability.name: Thick Skin
ability.bonus: Tahm Kench ignores damage from all sources.

ability.name: Truestrike
ability.bonus: Talon stabs his target, striking them for a percent of his attack damage. If this kills them, Talon becomes unstoppable and untargetable while he leaps to the enemy with the lowest Armor.

ability.name: Sporecloud Dart
ability.bonus: Teemo fires a dart at his target that explodes into a cloud of spores on contact, poisoning nearby enemies. Poisoned enemies take magic damage over a few seconds and are blinded for the duration.

ability.name: Wild Cards
ability.bonus: Twisted Fate throws three cards in a cone that deal magic damage to each enemy they pass through.

ability.name: Butterfly Burst
ability.bonus: Veigar blasts the lowest health enemy with a burst of energy, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Veigar permanently gains spell power.

ability.name: Denting Blow
ability.bonus: Vi's attack blasts through her target, dealing magic damage to all enemies in a cone and reducing their armor for 8 seconds.

ability.name: Crushing Blow
ability.bonus: Wukong slams his target with his staff, dealing a percent of his Attack Damage as physical damage and stunning them for a few seconds.

ability.name: Striking Steel
ability.bonus: Yasuo strikes forward two hexes, dealing a percent of his Attack Damage as physical damage and applying on-hit effects.

ability.name: Seal Fate
ability.bonus: Yone strikes along a path in front of him, dealing magic damage split between all enemies hit. Enemies hit are marked for death, reducing their Armor and Magic Resist by 60%. Yone's spell is then replaced with Unforgotten until there are no remaining enemies marked for death. Unforgotten (20 mana): Yone dashes to the lowest health enemy that is marked for death, killing them instantly.

ability.name: Zoomies
ability.bonus: Yuumi dashes next to a low health ally, healing them for a percent of their missing health and granting them attack speed for 5 seconds. She then repeats this for the furthest ally.

ability.name: Rewind Fate
ability.bonus: Zilean places a protective Time Rune on the 2 allies with the lowest Health. When they would die, they instead resurrect after 3.5 seconds, returning to combat with some health and shredding all negative effects. After resurrecting, they have 50% bonus Attack Speed for the rest of combat.

ability.name: Voice of Lightning
ability.bonus: Aurelion Sol breathes lightning in a line towards the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage and Overcharging all enemies hit for 10 seconds. If an enemy is already overcharged, Aurelion Sol consumes the effect and deals 50% bonus damage.

ability.name: Dragonfire Pillar
ability.bonus: After a brief delay, Brand erupts the ground under the enemy with the highest Attack Speed in flames, dealing magic damage to enemies within. If an enemy is caught in the epicenter, they are stunned.

ability.name: Unbreakable
ability.bonus: Braum faces the farthest enemy and raises his shield for 4 seconds, absorbing and stopping all incoming missiles and reducing his damage taken from that direction.

ability.name: Rupture
ability.bonus: Chogath ruptures a large area, dealing magic damage and knocking up all enemies within. Fabled Bonus: Chogath additionally knocks up all enemies on the board.

ability.name: Fortune's Guillotine
ability.bonus: Darius dunks an enemy, dealing magic damag. While dunking, Darius is unstoppable. If this kills the target, Darius immediately casts again dealing 20% reduced damage.

ability.name: Pale Cascade
ability.bonus: Diana shields herself against damage over 4 seconds and summons orbs to orbit around her. These orbs explode for magic damage when they contact an enemy, refreshing her shield when the final one explodes.

ability.name: Ascend
ability.bonus: Kayle Ascends, causing her attacks to launch waves that deal bonus magic damage to enemies hit.

ability.name: Wither
ability.bonus: Nasus withers the enemy with the highest percent health, dealing magic damage over 5 seconds and slowing their attack speed and movement speed by 50% for the duration.

ability.name: Impact Crater
ability.bonus: Nautilus erupts the ground beneath his target, knocking them up and stunning them and dealing magic damage. Fabled Bonus: Nautilus also grants himself a shield that reduces incoming damage by 75% for 5 seconds.

ability.name: Pop Blossom
ability.bonus: Neeko throws a seed at a random target that explodes for magic damage three times, with each explosion increasing the radius by one hex. Fabled Bonus: The third explosion is empowered dealing bonus magic damage.

ability.name: Ragnarok
ability.bonus: Olaf gains bonus attack speed, immunity to crowd control, and his attacks cleave in a cone in front of him for the rest of combat.

ability.name: Stampede
ability.bonus: Ornn summons an elemental from behind the furthest enemy to travel towards him, slowing the Attack Speed of enemies hit by 50% for 3 seconds and dealing magic damage. If the elemental runs into Ornn, he headbutts it, redirecting it towards another distant enemy, stunning them and dealing magic damage.

ability.name: Grand Entrance
ability.bonus: Rakan dashes next to the farthest enemy within his range, Disarming all units he passes through and taunting his target. Rakan then creates a shield on himself for 4 seconds.

ability.name: Inferno Trigger
ability.bonus: Samira dashes and becomes unstoppable, unleashing shots at 3 enemies within 2.5 hexes for 2 seconds (Total shots: 24). For the duration, Samira gains 100% dodge chance.

ability.name: Dragon's Descent
ability.bonus: Shyvana transforms into her Dragon Form, flying away from her current target. While in Dragon Form Shyvana gains 90% bonus Health, some Attack Damage, and her basic attacks become ranged attacks that deal bonus magic damage over 2 seconds on hit.

ability.name: On The Hunt
ability.bonus: Sivir rallies her allies, granting them Attack Speed for 5 seconds. Sivir gains bonus Attack Damage for the duration.

ability.name: Draconic Ascension
ability.bonus: Swain transforms into his dragon form for 6 seconds, gaining maximum health and dealing magic damage per second to enemies within range. While in this form, every 2 seconds Swain breaths fire in a cone in front of him, dealing magic damage, burning enemies for 25% of their maximum health as true damage over 10 seconds, and reducing healing by 50% for the duration.

ability.name: Rapid Fire
ability.bonus: Tristana excites her Dragon, increasing her Attack Speed and dealing bonus magic damage on hit for 3 seconds.

ability.name: Spinning Slash
ability.bonus: Tryndamere spins towards the most enemies in a line dealing 100% of his Attack Damage to enemies in his path and empowering his next three attacks to do additional damage.

ability.name: Transfusion
ability.bonus: Vladimir deals magic damage to his target. All nearby allies are healed for 40% of damage dealt.

ability.name: Featherstorm
ability.bonus: Xayah leaps into the air becoming untargetable, invulnerable, and throwing out a fan of feather daggers, dealing a percent of her Attack Damage as physical damage to enemies within the cone. Xayah then recalls her feathers, striking enemies hit for magic damage per feather.

ability.name: Contempt for the Weak
ability.bonus: Passive: Zed leaps to the enemy back line at the start of combat. Every third attack, Zed deals bonus magic damage and steals a percent of the target's current Attack Damage.

ability.name: Hallowed Ground
ability.bonus: Morgana hallows the ground beneath her target, dealing magic damage to enemies within over 5 seconds and shredding their Magic Resistance and reducing their Attack Damage by 40% while they remain inside.

ability.name: Dance of Dread
ability.bonus: Wolf mauls Kindred's target, dealing magic damage and reducing healing by 50% to her target for 5 seconds, while Lamb leaps away from Kindred's target.

ability.name: Phantom Undertow
ability.bonus: Pyke dashes behind the furthest enemy, creating an afterimage that deals magic damage and stuns enemies it passes through for a few seconds.
